0
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Collectors 编译

1
00:01:15,226 --> 00:01:17,570
船长！
Captain！

2
00:01:37,697 --> 00:01:39,460
你究竟是谁？
Who are you？

3
00:01:59,032 --> 00:02:02,055
加地斯，西班牙

4
00:02:32,452 --> 00:02:33,646
这是怎么回事？
What is this？

5
00:02:33,786 --> 00:02:36,454
国王陛下，他是被渔网捞上来的
Your Majesty，caught him up in a fishing net. 

6
00:02:36,786 --> 00:02:37,454
一个渔网
A fishing net. 

7
00:02:37,456 --> 00:02:38,855
陛下，他一直在讲故事
Sire，he's been telling stories. 

8
00:02:38,856 --> 00:02:39,524
故事说...
Stories that...

9
00:02:39,526 --> 00:02:41,460
我们相信他找到了...
We believe he's found a...

10
00:02:49,435 --> 00:02:51,369
庞塞德莱昂
Ponce de Leon. 

11
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:55,973
说他找到庞塞德莱昂的船了
Says he found Ponce de Leon's ship. 

12
00:02:55,975 --> 00:02:57,410
或是搭过那艘船
Or sailed on it. 

13
00:02:57,412 --> 00:02:58,843
不，我跟你说过
No，I told you，

14
00:02:58,845 --> 00:03:01,243
庞塞德莱昂死于两百年前
Ponce de Leon died 200 years ago. 

15
00:03:01,247 --> 00:03:04,908
但他死于寻找某样东西，对吧？
Aye，but he died searching for something，didn't he？

16
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:09,216
不老泉
The Fountain of Youth. 

17
00:03:14,327 --> 00:03:16,090
你航行可以多快？
How soon can you sail？

18
00:03:17,397 --> 00:03:19,524
顺着海水潮汐
With the tide. 

19
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:32,449
加勒比海盗 4：惊涛骇浪

20
00:03:37,584 --> 00:03:38,778
在这里！幸运石楠！
Over here！Lucky heather！

21
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:42,000
伦敦，英格兰

22
00:03:40,019 --> 00:03:41,987
海盗剑，海盗剑
Pirate swords！Pirate swords！

23
00:03:42,155 --> 00:03:43,923
海盗今天绞刑
Pirate's execution today. 

24
00:03:43,924 --> 00:03:45,690
快来看他吊死！
Watch him swing！

25
00:03:45,692 --> 00:03:47,557
海盗木偶！
Pirate puppets！

26
00:03:48,194 --> 00:03:49,218
接招！
Take that，you！

27
00:03:49,362 --> 00:03:51,295
爸爸，快点，不然看不到绞刑！
Hurry，Papa，or we'll miss the hanging！

28
00:03:51,297 --> 00:03:53,145
不是绞刑，宝贝，是审讯
It's not a hanging，dear，it's a trial. 

29
00:03:53,147 --> 00:03:54,994
今天下午才是绞刑
The hanging comes this afternoon. 

30
00:03:55,168 --> 00:03:56,795
海盗今天被绞死！
Pirate hanging today！

31
00:03:58,738 --> 00:04:01,639
起来，快点
Come on. Up you get. 

32
00:04:02,742 --> 00:04:04,539
海盗，向前走
Move along，pirate. 

33
00:04:05,245 --> 00:04:08,078
还是我应该说“海盗船长”？
Or should I say，“Captain Pirate”？

34
00:04:09,249 --> 00:04:12,583
快点，走吧，往上走
Come on. Come on！Up you go. 

35
00:04:12,585 --> 00:04:14,450
肃静！秩序！
Quiet！Order！

36
00:04:15,922 --> 00:04:17,321
肃静！
Quiet！

37
00:04:18,124 --> 00:04:19,921
现在出庭的是
Now appearing before the court，

38
00:04:20,059 --> 00:04:23,427
臭名昭著，声名狼藉的海盗，掠夺者
the notorious and infamous pirate，pillager，

39
00:04:23,429 --> 00:04:24,196
和强盗...
and highwayman...

40
00:04:24,197 --> 00:04:24,962
安静！
Quiet！

41
00:04:24,964 --> 00:04:26,659
...杰克斯派罗船长！
...Captain Jack Sparrow！

42
00:04:30,903 --> 00:04:32,737
我跟你们说过，我叫吉卜斯！
I told you，the name's Gibbs！

43
00:04:32,739 --> 00:04:34,572
贾夏密吉卜斯！
Joshamee Gibbs！

44
00:04:34,574 --> 00:04:35,555
要说几次...
How many times...

45
00:04:35,557 --> 00:04:36,540
注意，注意！
Hear ye，hear ye！

46
00:04:36,542 --> 00:04:37,975
主持这次审判
Presiding over these trials，

47
00:04:37,977 --> 00:04:39,907
全体起立
all rise and attend，

48
00:04:39,907 --> 00:04:43,609
尊敬的史密斯法官
the Right Honorable Justice Smith！

49
00:04:53,259 --> 00:04:55,159
尊敬的阁下
My dear sir. 

50
00:04:58,331 --> 00:05:00,128
肃静！
Quiet！

51
00:05:01,701 --> 00:05:03,692
现在...
Now...

52
00:05:05,104 --> 00:05:07,072
...我们在这里做什么？
...what do we have here？

53
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,537
杰克？
Jack？

54
00:05:08,675 --> 00:05:10,165
闭嘴！
Shut up！

55
00:05:11,010 --> 00:05:11,977
我不认识他
I don't recognize him. 

56
00:05:12,111 --> 00:05:13,708
没有必要
Not necessary. 

57
00:05:13,710 --> 00:05:15,446
你要说什么？
You were saying？

58
00:05:15,448 --> 00:05:18,076
我不是杰克斯派罗
Jack Sparrow is not my name. 

59
00:05:18,251 --> 00:05:20,151
我是贾夏密吉卜斯
My name is Joshamee Gibbs. 

60
00:05:20,286 --> 00:05:22,015
是这样吗？
Is that so？

61
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:23,655
这里说你是杰克斯派罗
It says Jack Sparrow here. 

62
00:05:23,657 --> 00:05:25,323
我跟他们说过
I told 'em. 

63
00:05:25,325 --> 00:05:26,973
我不是杰克斯派罗
I'm not Jack Sparrow，

64
00:05:26,975 --> 00:05:28,620
如果有助于我的案子
who I would be happy to identify to the court

65
00:05:28,628 --> 00:05:30,145
我很乐意当庭指认
if it would help my case. 

66
00:05:30,147 --> 00:05:31,662
这是拙劣的狡辩
I think that would be a poor defense，

67
00:05:31,664 --> 00:05:33,012
除非你想要再挨棍子
unless you want to be bludgeoned again 

68
00:05:33,013 --> 00:05:34,360
像格陵兰海豹一样
like a harp seal. 

69
00:05:36,069 --> 00:05:37,534
犯人声称
The prisoner claims of being innocent 

70
00:05:37,535 --> 00:05:38,998
他不是杰克斯派罗
to being Jack Sparrow. 

71
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,898
你们怎么判决？
How do you find？

72
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,169
不审判？
No trial？

73
00:05:42,170 --> 00:05:43,439
不是该审查证据...
But aren't we here to examine the evidence...

74
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,734
陪审长，他有罪吗？
Foreman，your finding. Guilty？

75
00:05:45,878 --> 00:05:47,743
有罪意味着他会被绞死
Guilty verdict means he'll hang. 

76
00:05:49,482 --> 00:05:50,529
绞死他！
Hang him！

77
00:05:50,530 --> 00:05:51,575
把他吊起来！
String him up！

78
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:55,366
有罪？
Guilty？

79
00:05:55,368 --> 00:05:56,379
这不公平！
That's not fair！

80
00:05:56,522 --> 00:05:57,750
闭嘴
Shut it. 

81
00:05:59,092 --> 00:06:00,960
贾夏密吉卜斯
Joshamee Gibbs，

82
00:06:00,962 --> 00:06:02,960
你被当成是杰克斯派罗
the crime of which you've been found guilty of

83
00:06:02,962 --> 00:06:06,430
被判有罪是无罪的
is being innocent of being Jack Sparrow. 

84
00:06:06,432 --> 00:06:09,768
我在此改判你无期徒刑
I hereby commute your sentence，

85
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:11,168
待在监狱里
and order that you be imprisoned

86
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:12,654
度过你悲惨
for the remainder of your miserable，

87
00:06:12,656 --> 00:06:14,137
垂死无助的余生
moribund，mutton-chopped life. 

88
00:06:14,173 --> 00:06:15,140
什么？
What？！

89
00:06:15,142 --> 00:06:16,107
绞死他！
Hang him！

90
00:06:16,242 --> 00:06:16,839
绞死他！
Hang him！

91
00:06:16,841 --> 00:06:17,436
定谳
There. 

92
00:06:18,177 --> 00:06:19,559
胡言乱语！
Balderdash！

93
00:06:19,561 --> 00:06:20,251
把他吊起来！
String him up！

94
00:06:20,252 --> 00:06:20,941
绞死他！
Hang him high！

95
00:06:22,582 --> 00:06:23,913
安排马车
Means shall be arranged 

96
00:06:23,915 --> 00:06:25,244
移送这名犯人
to transport this prisoner

97
00:06:25,385 --> 00:06:27,410
到伦敦塔
to the Tower of London. 

98
00:06:38,798 --> 00:06:40,231
感激不尽
Thanks very much. 

99
00:06:44,604 --> 00:06:45,798
谢啦
Ta. 

100
00:06:49,609 --> 00:06:50,923
快点
Come on. 

101
00:06:50,925 --> 00:06:52,237
上车
Get up there. 

102
00:06:54,614 --> 00:06:56,377
上去！
Get up！

103
00:07:01,053 --> 00:07:02,822
这下好了
Hell's teeth. 

104
00:07:02,824 --> 00:07:04,822
我们都进监狱了
Now we're both headed for prison. 

105
00:07:04,824 --> 00:07:06,250
不用担心
Not to worry. 

106
00:07:06,252 --> 00:07:07,691
我贿赂了车夫
I've paid off the driver. 

107
00:07:07,693 --> 00:07:10,297
十分钟后，我们会在伦敦城外
Ten minutes，we'll be outside London Town， 

108
00:07:10,296 --> 00:07:11,163
有马匹等着
horses waiting.

109
00:07:11,164 --> 00:07:12,831
今晚，骑到海边
Tonight，we make the coast. 

110
00:07:12,832 --> 00:07:15,198
然后就是找一艘船的事了
Then it's just a matter of finding a ship. 

111
00:07:16,469 --> 00:07:18,070
一切都在计划中，是吧？
All part of the plan，yes？

112
00:07:18,072 --> 00:07:19,271
没说错
Exactly. 

113
00:07:19,272 --> 00:07:21,372
今天一早我就来到伦敦城
I arrived in London Town just this morning

114
00:07:21,374 --> 00:07:23,008
要从绞刑架
to rescue one Joshamee Gibbs 

115
00:07:23,009 --> 00:07:24,642
救出贾夏密吉卜斯
from one appointment with the gallows. 

116
00:07:24,644 --> 00:07:26,577
看到你还活着
Seeing as how you're still alive，

117
00:07:26,579 --> 00:07:29,980
我会说到现在为止计划很成功
I'd say it's all been very successful thus far.

118
00:07:29,982 --> 00:07:31,315
吉卜斯，你出什么事了？
What happened to you，Gibbs？

119
00:07:31,317 --> 00:07:32,684
我以为你在别处工作
I thought you were employed elsewhere 

120
00:07:32,685 --> 00:07:34,051
或忙其他的
or otherwise engaged. 

121
00:07:34,053 --> 00:07:35,854
是啊，但我一直偷偷打听
Aye. But I always listened like a thief 

122
00:07:35,855 --> 00:07:37,655
黑珍珠号的消息
for news of the Black Pearl. 

123
00:07:37,657 --> 00:07:40,257
但没有人知道她停靠在哪个港口
Nobody's seen where she might next make port. 

124
00:07:40,259 --> 00:07:42,461
然后，我听到传闻：
Then，I hear a rumor:

125
00:07:42,462 --> 00:07:44,279
杰克斯派罗带着船来伦敦
Jack Sparrow's in London with a ship 

126
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,097
正在寻找船员
and looking for a crew. 

127
00:07:46,098 --> 00:07:47,012
哪有
Am not. 

128
00:07:47,014 --> 00:07:47,926
我听到的就是这些
But that's what I heard. 

129
00:07:47,928 --> 00:07:49,131
事实是
Fact is，

130
00:07:49,132 --> 00:07:50,334
你今晚要签约雇用船员
you're signing up men tonight. 

131
00:07:50,336 --> 00:07:52,002
酒吧名字叫“船长的女儿”
Pub called The Captain's Daughter. 

132
00:07:52,004 --> 00:07:53,698
哪有
Am not！

133
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:55,406
是呀，我想这有点古怪
Well，I thought it a bit odd，

134
00:07:55,408 --> 00:07:59,977
但是，你从不是最可预测的人
but then，you've never been the most predictable of sorts. 

135
00:07:59,979 --> 00:08:01,412
告诉我
Tell me something. 

136
00:08:01,414 --> 00:08:03,248
有另一个杰克斯派罗
There is another Jack Sparrow 

137
00:08:03,249 --> 00:08:05,082
在招摇撞骗？
out there sullying my good name？

138
00:08:05,084 --> 00:08:06,218
冒牌货
An impostor.

139
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:07,351
没错
Indeed. 

140
00:08:07,353 --> 00:08:09,288
不过...
But...

141
00:08:09,289 --> 00:08:11,222
是有一艘船的冒牌货
an impostor with a ship. 

142
00:08:11,224 --> 00:08:13,958
而且需要船员
And in need of a crew. 

143
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:16,994
正巧，我也需要
Which，as fate would have it，so am I. 

144
00:08:16,996 --> 00:08:18,762
杰克，那你呢？
What about you，Jack？

145
00:08:18,764 --> 00:08:19,988
上次我听说
Last I heard，

146
00:08:19,990 --> 00:08:22,766
你拚命寻找不老泉
you were hell-bentto find the Fountain of Youth. 

147
00:08:22,768 --> 00:08:24,258
找到了？
Any luck？

148
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:29,440
发生要求有敏锐的洞察力
Circumstances arose and forced a compelling insight

149
00:08:29,442 --> 00:08:31,542
关于谨慎以及勇气的情况
regarding discretion and valor. 

150
00:08:31,544 --> 00:08:33,108
意思是，你放弃了
Meaning，you gave up. 

151
00:08:33,110 --> 00:08:34,672
我没有
I did not. 

152
00:08:34,814 --> 00:08:36,298
我就和以前一样坚定
I am just as bent as ever. 

153
00:08:36,299 --> 00:08:37,781
非常坚定
Hellishly so. 

154
00:08:37,783 --> 00:08:40,504
我会喝到不老泉的，吉卜斯先生
I shall taste those waters，Master Gibbs. 

155
00:08:40,506 --> 00:08:42,584
记住我的话
Mark my words. 

156
00:08:45,358 --> 00:08:46,382
哦，这么快就到啦
Short trip. 

157
00:08:55,268 --> 00:08:58,362
一切都在计划中，是吧？
All part of the plan，yes？

158
00:09:01,507 --> 00:09:02,565
不是
No. 

159
00:10:30,896 --> 00:10:34,059
你就是杰克斯派罗？
You are Jack Sparrow？

160
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,928
你忘了加上“船长”
There should be a“Captain”in there somewhere. 

161
00:10:36,936 --> 00:10:39,461
我听说过你
I've heard of you. 

162
00:10:39,605 --> 00:10:41,664
想必你知道我是谁
And you know who I am. 

163
00:10:42,675 --> 00:10:43,972
很面熟
Face is familiar. 

164
00:10:43,974 --> 00:10:45,269
我有恐吓过你？
Have I threatened you before？

165
00:10:45,378 --> 00:10:46,362
在你面前的是
You are in the presence of 

166
00:10:46,363 --> 00:10:47,346
乔治奥古斯汀
George Augustus，

167
00:10:47,348 --> 00:10:49,313
伯伦瑞克-吕讷堡公爵
Duke of Brunswick-Luneburg，

168
00:10:49,315 --> 00:10:50,816
神圣罗马帝国的
Archtreasurer and Prince-elector  

169
00:10:50,817 --> 00:10:52,316
财务大臣和王子选侯
of the Holy Roman Empire，

170
00:10:52,318 --> 00:10:54,419
英国和爱尔兰的国王
King of Great Britain and Ireland，

171
00:10:54,418 --> 00:10:55,719
你的国王
and of you. 

172
00:10:57,189 --> 00:10:58,440
没听说过
Doesn't ring a bell. 

173
00:10:58,442 --> 00:10:59,690
我听说
I am informed

174
00:10:59,692 --> 00:11:01,922
你是来伦敦
you have come to London to procure 

175
00:11:01,923 --> 00:11:04,152
招募船员
a crew for your ship. 

176
00:11:04,964 --> 00:11:06,431
邪恶的谣言，并非事实
Vicious rumor. Not true. 

177
00:11:06,599 --> 00:11:08,216
那你自称杰克斯派罗
Then you lied to me when you told me 

178
00:11:08,217 --> 00:11:09,833
就是骗我咯
you were Jack Sparrow.

179
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:11,519
我是杰克斯派罗
I am Jack Sparrow，

180
00:11:11,521 --> 00:11:13,203
但我没有招募船员
but I'm not here to procure a crew. 

181
00:11:13,205 --> 00:11:15,006
那是...
That is...

182
00:11:15,007 --> 00:11:16,807
另一个人
someone else. 

183
00:11:16,809 --> 00:11:21,045
另一个叫杰克斯派罗的人
Someone else named Jack Sparrow. 

184
00:11:21,047 --> 00:11:23,242
你们给我找错人了
You've brought me the wrong wastrel. 

185
00:11:23,382 --> 00:11:25,032
找到真的
Find the proper one 

186
00:11:25,034 --> 00:11:26,681
然后解决这个冒牌货
and dispose of this impostor. 

187
00:11:26,819 --> 00:11:27,849
不，等等
No，wait，wait，wait. 

188
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:28,878
等一下
Hang on a minute. 

189
00:11:29,021 --> 00:11:30,221
我是杰克斯派罗
I'm Jack Sparrow，

190
00:11:30,222 --> 00:11:31,421
独一无二
the one and only. 

191
00:11:31,557 --> 00:11:33,252
而且我在伦敦
And I am in London. 

192
00:11:33,392 --> 00:11:35,451
招募船员
To procure a crew. 

193
00:11:35,628 --> 00:11:37,323
准备启航
To undertake a voyage

194
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:38,165
前往不老泉...
to the Fountain...

195
00:11:38,167 --> 00:11:38,897
你说什么？
What？

196
00:11:39,031 --> 00:11:41,312
谁来拿掉那些
Will someone please remove these 

197
00:11:41,313 --> 00:11:43,593
讨厌的锁链？
infernal chains？

198
00:11:43,736 --> 00:11:44,896
来，来
Come，come. 

199
00:11:47,373 --> 00:11:49,773
我们知道你有一张地图
We know you're in possession of a map. 

200
00:11:49,909 --> 00:11:51,491
没收地图
So confiscate the map，

201
00:11:51,493 --> 00:11:53,072
然后绞死他
and to the gallows with him！

