397
00:26:39,864 --> 00:26:41,627
却没有我厉害
but cannot，in fact，hold a candle to，

398
00:26:41,766 --> 00:26:43,233
我才是杰克斯派罗船长
I am Captain Jack Sparrow. 

399
00:27:20,438 --> 00:27:22,998
你怎么能说我利用了你？
How can you say I used you？

400
00:27:23,141 --> 00:27:25,336
你明白的很
You know exactly how. 

401
00:27:25,477 --> 00:27:28,605
我知道，但你怎么能这么说？
I know，but how can you say it？

402
00:27:33,251 --> 00:27:34,997
怎么回事？
So，what is it？

403
00:27:34,999 --> 00:27:36,743
什么怎么回事？
What is what？

404
00:27:36,921 --> 00:27:38,411
不老泉啊
About the Fountain. 

405
00:27:41,026 --> 00:27:42,050
你都知道什么？
What do you know？

406
00:27:44,029 --> 00:27:45,621
你不会是恰好有
You don't happen to be in possession

407
00:27:45,730 --> 00:27:48,995
庞塞德莱昂的两只银杯吧？
of two silver chalices，circa Ponce de Leon？

408
00:27:49,701 --> 00:27:50,634
没有
No. 

409
00:27:50,636 --> 00:27:51,566
我想也没有
Thought not. 

410
00:27:51,703 --> 00:27:53,517
为什么？
Why？

411
00:27:53,519 --> 00:27:55,332
我听到一些说法
I hear stories. 

412
00:27:55,473 --> 00:27:57,304
谣传
Rumors. 

413
00:27:57,409 --> 00:27:59,570
你一定知道那个仪式
You are，of course，aware of the ritual. 

414
00:28:00,545 --> 00:28:01,637
对，我知道
Yes，I am. 

415
00:28:03,982 --> 00:28:05,347
是什么仪式？
What is it？

416
00:28:05,349 --> 00:28:06,712
需要什么？
What is required？

417
00:28:11,322 --> 00:28:13,313
一只人鱼，杰克
A mermaid，Jack. 

418
00:28:21,299 --> 00:28:22,698
你们搞错了
There's been a mistake. 

419
00:28:22,834 --> 00:28:24,010
是无期徒刑
It's a life sentence，

420
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:25,229
不是死刑
not death. 

421
00:28:25,361 --> 00:28:26,361
是无期！
Life！

422
00:28:31,776 --> 00:28:33,442
巴船长
Barbossa. 

423
00:28:33,444 --> 00:28:35,109
各位，谢谢你们
Thank you，gentlemen. 

424
00:28:35,246 --> 00:28:38,238
我想你会绑绞绳吧
I trust you can tie a noose. 

425
00:28:38,383 --> 00:28:39,782
这是很困难的事
That's a hard thing，

426
00:28:39,918 --> 00:28:42,910
逼一个人绑自己的绞绳
forcing a man to twis this own hanging rope. 

427
00:28:43,755 --> 00:28:46,588
你必须为你的行为付出代价
You must lie in your bed the way you made it. 

428
00:28:48,426 --> 00:28:49,791
你是怎么了？
What's happened to you？

429
00:28:49,928 --> 00:28:51,646
杰克斯派罗呢？
Where be Jack Sparrow？

430
00:28:51,648 --> 00:28:53,364
他逃走了
He escaped. 

431
00:28:53,465 --> 00:28:54,932
吉卜斯，我在赶时间
I'm on a tight schedule，Gibbs. 

432
00:28:55,066 --> 00:28:57,432
天佑号天一亮就启航
The HMS Providence sets sail at first light. 

433
00:28:57,569 --> 00:28:59,730
如果你不想尸体被吊在这里
If you do not care to watch it hanging here dead，

434
00:28:59,871 --> 00:29:01,896
满嘴都是苍蝇...
with a mouth full of flies...

435
00:29:03,541 --> 00:29:05,168
...现在就说
...speak now. 

436
00:29:06,911 --> 00:29:08,156
带上我吧
Take me with you. 

437
00:29:08,157 --> 00:29:09,546
去哪儿都行...
Any point of the compass...

438
00:29:09,547 --> 00:29:11,965
吉卜斯，带你去哪呀？
Take you where，Gibbs？

439
00:29:11,966 --> 00:29:14,382
不老泉？是吗？
The Fountain？Aye？

440
00:29:14,486 --> 00:29:17,512
杰克也要去那儿吧？
Is that where Jack be headed？

441
00:29:17,689 --> 00:29:21,716
吉卜斯，你能给我什么？
Have you anything you can offer me，Gibbs？

442
00:29:21,826 --> 00:29:23,384
什么都没有？
Anything at all？

443
00:29:25,163 --> 00:29:26,909
我说话算话
Upon me naked word，

444
00:29:26,910 --> 00:29:28,655
你看不到日出了
you'll not see the dawn. 

445
00:29:36,708 --> 00:29:38,437
拿过来
Hand it over. 

446
00:29:43,181 --> 00:29:44,328
你这笨蛋！
You fool！

447
00:29:44,330 --> 00:29:45,479
我正好有足够时间
I had just enough time

448
00:29:45,617 --> 00:29:48,108
研究这些阴间的符号
to study those infernal circles. 

449
00:29:48,253 --> 00:29:50,568
每条路线，每个目的地
Every route，every destination. 

450
00:29:50,570 --> 00:29:52,883
全都在…这
All safe... in here. 

451
00:29:54,392 --> 00:29:58,419
吉卜斯先生，欢迎加入皇家海军
Welcome back to His Majesty's navy，Master Gibbs. 

452
00:30:11,509 --> 00:30:13,500
起床了，水手！
Show a leg，sailor！

453
00:30:13,645 --> 00:30:14,873
是，长官
Aye，sir. 

454
00:30:16,414 --> 00:30:17,711
什么？
What？

455
00:30:17,849 --> 00:30:19,450
这误会大了
There's been a horrible mistake. 

456
00:30:19,452 --> 00:30:21,046
继续走
Keep moving. 

457
00:30:22,554 --> 00:30:24,039
我不应该在这里
I'm not supposed to be here. 

458
00:30:24,041 --> 00:30:25,523
很多人在船上醒来
Many a man's woken up at sea，

459
00:30:25,657 --> 00:30:27,591
都搞不清楚状况
no idea what，when，wherefore or why. 

460
00:30:27,759 --> 00:30:28,874
不记得前一晚
No memory of the night afore，

461
00:30:28,876 --> 00:30:29,989
在哪签了什么合同
whence he signed up

462
00:30:30,128 --> 00:30:31,652
还把钱通通拿去买醉
and drank away all his bonus money. 

463
00:30:31,796 --> 00:30:33,787
不，老兄，你不明白
No，no，no. You don't understand，mate. 

464
00:30:33,898 --> 00:30:35,115
我是杰克斯派罗船长
I'm Captain Jack Sparrow. 

465
00:30:35,117 --> 00:30:36,332
独此一家，如假包换
The original. The only. 

466
00:30:36,467 --> 00:30:37,747
我是石头，幸会了
Scrum，and the pleasure's all mine. 

467
00:30:37,749 --> 00:30:39,027
继续走
Now，keep moving. 

468
00:30:47,545 --> 00:30:49,012
石头
Scrum. 

469
00:30:49,147 --> 00:30:51,377
靠过来
Get your elbows in！

470
00:30:53,885 --> 00:30:55,750
为什么那有一个玻璃棺？
Why is there a glass coffin？

471
00:30:55,887 --> 00:30:58,355
看来像我管的？
Do I look like a man in charge？

472
00:30:58,489 --> 00:30:59,957
我在哪里？
Where am I？

473
00:30:59,959 --> 00:31:01,424
抱歉，斯派罗船长
'Scuse me，Captain Sparrow，sir. 

474
00:31:01,559 --> 00:31:03,220
我很荣幸欢迎你登上
I be right honoredto welcome you aboard

475
00:31:03,361 --> 00:31:04,994
臭名狼藉的
our world-renowned vessel of infamy，

476
00:31:04,996 --> 00:31:06,626
安妮王后复仇号
Queen Anne's Revenge. 

477
00:31:10,034 --> 00:31:11,695
黑胡子的船
Blackbeard. 

478
00:31:28,052 --> 00:31:29,917
干活
Work！

479
00:31:33,725 --> 00:31:35,591
他是一个奇怪的家伙
He's a curious one. 

480
00:31:35,593 --> 00:31:37,454
他是活死人
He's been zombiefied. 

481
00:31:37,456 --> 00:31:38,728
啥？

482
00:31:38,730 --> 00:31:40,254
活死人
Zombiefied. 

483
00:31:40,398 --> 00:31:42,144
黑胡子干的
Blackbeard's doing. 

484
00:31:42,146 --> 00:31:43,890
每个头儿都是
All the officers are the same. 

485
00:31:44,035 --> 00:31:45,764
好让他们更顺从
Makes 'em more compliant. 

486
00:31:47,038 --> 00:31:49,006
而且脾气一样坏
And perpetually ill-tempered. 

487
00:31:50,708 --> 00:31:52,005
快点，用力擦洗
Come on. Scrub. 

488
00:31:52,007 --> 00:31:53,302
是
Yeah. 

489
00:32:00,385 --> 00:32:04,014
拉！拉！用力拉！
Pull！Pull！Pull！

490
00:32:08,559 --> 00:32:11,119
航行了五天，至少
Five days underway，at least. 

491
00:32:11,262 --> 00:32:15,096
对，你从海水味道闻出来的？
Aye. You can tell thatby the smell of the sea？

492
00:32:15,233 --> 00:32:16,962
是船员的臭味
Smell of the crew. 

493
00:32:20,538 --> 00:32:23,632
喂，那可怜的混帐干了什么？
Oi. What did that poor sod do？

494
00:32:23,775 --> 00:32:25,800
我该怎样才不会这样？
And how can I make sure to not？

495
00:32:25,944 --> 00:32:28,276
他喔？是虔诚教徒
Him？Churchly fellow. 

496
00:32:28,413 --> 00:32:30,438
老念着万能的主啊
Always going on about the Lord Almighty. 

497
00:32:30,581 --> 00:32:32,310
宗教狂热份子在这艘船上？
Bible-thumper on this ship？

498
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:34,350
他以前是传教士
A missionary is his story. 

499
00:32:34,485 --> 00:32:37,249
我听说他是在一次劫掠中被抓来
What I heard was he got captured in a raid. 

500
00:32:37,355 --> 00:32:40,256
船上其他人全被杀了，除了他
Rest of the ship got killed，but not 'im. 

501
00:32:40,358 --> 00:32:41,689
大副不肯杀死他
First mate wouldn't let it happen

502
00:32:41,826 --> 00:32:44,522
因为他信主
on account of his premier standing with the Lord. 

503
00:32:44,662 --> 00:32:46,865
大副以她的生命
A first mate sticking her neck 

504
00:32:46,867 --> 00:32:49,065
替囚犯求情
out for some prisoner. 

505
00:32:49,233 --> 00:32:50,825
那是你不能理解的
That you don't see. 

506
00:32:50,969 --> 00:32:53,665
“她”？大副是“女的”？
“Her”？First mate is a“her”？

507
00:32:53,805 --> 00:32:55,033
回去干活！
Back to work！

508
00:33:04,349 --> 00:33:06,613
稳稳地保持航向
Steady as she goes. 

509
00:33:20,832 --> 00:33:23,017
你是个无情的
You are a ruthless，

510
00:33:23,019 --> 00:33:25,201
卑鄙的，超级难搞的坏蛋
soulless，cross-grained cur. 

511
00:33:25,336 --> 00:33:27,082
我跟你说过我有一艘船
I told you I had a ship. 

512
00:33:27,084 --> 00:33:28,828
不对，是黑胡子有一艘船
No，Blackbeard has a ship，

513
00:33:28,973 --> 00:33:31,771
你害我变成囚犯
upon which I am now imprisoned. 

514
00:33:31,943 --> 00:33:33,911
杰克，我们办得到的
We can do this，Jack. 

515
00:33:34,045 --> 00:33:36,343
不老泉
The Fountain of Youth，

516
00:33:36,344 --> 00:33:38,641
你不也一直想找到
like you always wanted. 

517
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:40,033
黑胡子
Blackbeard. 

518
00:33:40,034 --> 00:33:41,315
爱德华汀奇
Edward Teach. 

519
00:33:41,317 --> 00:33:43,881
所有海盗都怕的海盗
The pirate all pirates fear. 

520
00:33:44,022 --> 00:33:46,183
有空就玩玩死人复活
Resurrector of the dead in his spare time. 

521
00:33:46,324 --> 00:33:47,758
他会听我的
He will listen to me. 

522
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:49,191
他谁也不会听
He listens to no one. 

523
00:33:49,327 --> 00:33:52,228
也许会听他亲生女儿的？
Maybe to his own daughter？

524
00:33:54,766 --> 00:33:57,701
女儿…亲生女儿？
Daughter as in... beget by？

525
00:33:58,569 --> 00:34:00,486
失散很久
Long-lost. 

526
00:34:00,487 --> 00:34:02,403
最近才相认
Recently found. 

527
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:06,374
全心全意爱她的老爸
Who loves her dear papa with all her soul. 

528
00:34:06,511 --> 00:34:07,541
他信这套鬼话？
He bought that？

529
00:34:07,543 --> 00:34:08,570
我说服了他
I sold that. 

530
00:34:16,020 --> 00:34:17,817
那么找不老泉是为了他
Then it's the Fountain of Youth for him，

531
00:34:17,989 --> 00:34:19,456
或者是为了你们
or him and you，

532
00:34:19,457 --> 00:34:20,922
不是为了我们
not you and me. 

533
00:34:20,992 --> 00:34:23,051
不，杰克，最棒的是
No，Jack，that's the best part. 

534
00:34:23,194 --> 00:34:25,253
他就快要死了
He will be dead. 

535
00:34:26,564 --> 00:34:28,964
你要亲手杀了他？
You'll be handling that part yourself，then？

536
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:31,364
有一个预言
There is a prophecy. 

537
00:34:31,469 --> 00:34:33,699
也许你不相信超自然现象
Maybe you don't believein the supernatural. 

538
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:34,960
喔，不
Oh，no，no. 

539
00:34:34,962 --> 00:34:36,296
这我倒是看过一两次
I've seen a thing or two. 

540
00:34:38,876 --> 00:34:42,835
这个预言是这样的：
The prophecy is this:

541
00:34:43,014 --> 00:34:46,814
黑胡子两周内将会死亡
Blackbeard will meet his death within a fortnight

542
00:34:46,951 --> 00:34:50,409
死在一个独腿者的手上
at the hands of a one-legged man. 

543
00:34:50,555 --> 00:34:52,750
所以他需要不老泉
That's why he needs the Fountain，Jack. 

544
00:35:09,073 --> 00:35:11,837
吉卜斯先生，我们没有地图
Master Gibbs，short we are a map. 

545
00:35:11,976 --> 00:35:13,523
也许你该好心
Perhaps you'd be so kindas 

546
00:35:13,523 --> 00:35:15,070
给我们一个航向
to provide us an heading. 

547
00:35:18,850 --> 00:35:20,943
麻烦倒杯酒给我
Be a gem and pour me a gulper. 

548
00:35:21,085 --> 00:35:22,803
不行，我们是私掠船
Nay. We be privateers， 

549
00:35:22,804 --> 00:35:24,521
不是海盗，吉卜斯先生
not pirates，Master Gibbs.

550
00:35:24,655 --> 00:35:26,782
我们奉国王陛下之名行事
And in the king's name，we behave as such. 

551
00:35:26,924 --> 00:35:29,757
遵命，船长
Aye，Captain. 

552
00:35:33,164 --> 00:35:35,962
吉卜斯，我们是在正确的航线上吗？
Be we on the proper course，Gibbs？

553
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,398
对，是正确的
Aye，it be proper. 

554
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:40,696
那就是证明
There's your proof. 

555
00:35:47,211 --> 00:35:48,508
西班牙舰队
The Spaniard. 

556
00:35:50,081 --> 00:35:53,236
全员注意，战斗位置
All hands！Battle stations！

557
00:35:53,238 --> 00:35:54,814
航向上风
Get to windward！

558
00:35:54,952 --> 00:35:56,482
全员注意，航向上风
All hands，windward！

559
00:35:56,484 --> 00:35:58,012
加固两点
Harden up two points！

560
00:35:58,156 --> 00:35:59,874
两点
Two points！

561
00:35:59,876 --> 00:36:01,592
炮手解开大炮
Cast loose the cannons！

562
00:36:05,563 --> 00:36:07,446
枪手，各就各位
Gunners，take posts！

563
00:36:07,448 --> 00:36:09,329
就位，枪手待命，长官
Take position！Gunners ready，sir！

564
00:36:09,467 --> 00:36:11,401
大炮解开，填弹
Out！Thrust！

565
00:36:11,403 --> 00:36:13,335
等待命令
Await orders. 

566
00:36:15,439 --> 00:36:16,804
稳住
Steady！

567
00:36:18,142 --> 00:36:19,734
填好炮弹，等待命令，长官
Guns armed，awaiting orders，sir. 

568
00:36:25,516 --> 00:36:29,077
长官，命令，长官？
Sir. Orders，sir？

569
00:36:35,693 --> 00:36:38,423
他甚至都没有转动他的头
He never so much as turned his head. 

570
00:36:38,563 --> 00:36:40,428
不老泉才是目标
The Fountain is the prize. 

571
00:36:40,565 --> 00:36:42,380
看来他们不想浪费时间
It appears we be not even worth the time 

572
00:36:42,381 --> 00:36:44,194
击沉我们
it'd take to sink us. 

573
00:36:44,335 --> 00:36:46,286
我们已经落后了
And now we've fallen behind. 

574
00:36:46,288 --> 00:36:48,237
全员注意，全速前进
All hands，make more sail！

575
00:36:48,372 --> 00:36:50,932
全员注意，全速前进
All hands，more sail！

576
00:36:51,075 --> 00:36:54,408
让我们乘风破浪吧
Ride hard between wind and tide！

577
00:37:04,388 --> 00:37:07,983
各位，我要说的可是叛变
The topic，gentlemen，is mutiny. 

578
00:37:08,759 --> 00:37:10,556
最可怕的叛变
Mutiny most foul. 

579
00:37:10,695 --> 00:37:13,000
是呀，我是来当杰克斯派罗的船员
Aye. I signed up to sail under Jack Sparrow，

580
00:37:13,002 --> 00:37:14,222
不是冒牌船长
not some pretender. 

581
00:37:14,365 --> 00:37:15,627
而且还是个女的
And a lady，at that. 

582
00:37:15,766 --> 00:37:17,961
也没人提到船上有活死人
And mention was failed to be made of this uncanny crew. 

583
00:37:18,102 --> 00:37:20,468
我怕得腿都软了
Make my toes curl，they do. 

584
00:37:20,605 --> 00:37:22,135
我拿到了
I got 'em.

585
00:37:22,137 --> 00:37:23,665
全部
All of them. 

586
00:37:23,841 --> 00:37:24,808
干得好
Well done. 

587
00:37:24,810 --> 00:37:25,775
好样的
Good lad. 

588
00:37:25,910 --> 00:37:28,344
我说，黑胡子
On to it，then. Blackbeard. 

589
00:37:28,512 --> 00:37:29,729
有什么习惯？
What are his habits？

590
00:37:29,731 --> 00:37:30,946
他多半都待在船长室
Stays mostly to his cabin. 

591
00:37:31,082 --> 00:37:33,880
没错，都待在船长室
That's right，mostly to his cabin. 

592
00:37:33,985 --> 00:37:35,600
没错，但是当他出来...
Yes，but when he comes out...

593
00:37:35,602 --> 00:37:37,216
他从来都不出来
He don't really come out. 

594
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,555
他总是会出来吧
He must come out sometime. 

595
00:37:41,425 --> 00:37:43,620
并没有
Not really，no. 

596
00:37:45,463 --> 00:37:47,158
有人和他航海过？
Any of you sail with him before？

597
00:37:47,298 --> 00:37:48,032
没，没有
No，no. 

598
00:37:48,034 --> 00:37:48,765
我从来没有
I've never. 

599
00:37:48,899 --> 00:37:49,923
绝对没有
Definitely not. 

600
00:37:50,067 --> 00:37:52,000
有人看过他？
Any of you seen him before？

601
00:37:52,002 --> 00:37:53,935
并没有，没有
Not really，no. 

602
00:37:55,539 --> 00:37:56,620
他待在船长室
Stays to his cabin，

603
00:37:56,622 --> 00:37:57,700
没人和他航海
no one sailed with him，

604
00:37:57,875 --> 00:37:59,900
没人见过他...
no one's seen him...

605
00:38:00,077 --> 00:38:01,645
各位，好消息
Good news，gentlemen. 

606
00:38:01,647 --> 00:38:03,212
这不是黑胡子的船
This is not Blackbeard's ship. 

607
00:38:03,214 --> 00:38:05,147
这不是安妮王后复仇号
This is not the Queen Anne's Revenge. 

608
00:38:05,149 --> 00:38:07,174
不对，这是安妮王后复仇号
No，this be the Queen Anne's Revenge，right enough. 

609
00:38:07,318 --> 00:38:08,785
你怎么知道？
How do you know？

610
00:38:08,919 --> 00:38:10,552
我看过船名
I've seen the name，

611
00:38:10,554 --> 00:38:12,184
就在船尾
on the back of the ship. 

612
00:38:15,426 --> 00:38:20,386
各位，各位伙伴...
Gentlemen，sirs，fellow conscriptees...

613
00:38:22,133 --> 00:38:24,260
...你们都被骗了
...you have been monstrously deceived. 

614
00:38:24,368 --> 00:38:27,350
我们被耍了？
We are decepted，then？

615
00:38:27,352 --> 00:38:28,532
没错
Yes. 

616
00:38:28,673 --> 00:38:31,608
你们都不知道目的地吧
You've nay been informed of a destination. 

617
00:38:31,709 --> 00:38:33,870
死亡就摆在我们面前了
Death lies before us

618
00:38:34,011 --> 00:38:36,429
因为我们正航向
as we sail 

619
00:38:36,430 --> 00:38:38,846
不老泉
for the Fountain of Youth. 

620
00:38:40,651 --> 00:38:42,346
情况不妙啊，伙计们
It would be a sorry plight，mates. 

621
00:38:42,486 --> 00:38:44,898
我们死定了
Death，for certain. 

622
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,616
那儿是幽灵的花园
The garden of darkened souls. 

623
00:38:46,724 --> 00:38:48,407
我们的葬生之地
Untimely our ends will be. 

624
00:38:48,409 --> 00:38:50,091
除非...
Unless...

625
00:38:50,261 --> 00:38:52,752
...我们抢下这艘船
...we take the ship. 

626
00:38:54,065 --> 00:38:57,626
我们抢下这艘船，现在！
We take the ship，then. Now！

627
00:39:01,839 --> 00:39:03,363
快去啊
Go on，then. 

628
00:39:04,141 --> 00:39:05,455
快帮忙，水手们！
Help me，shipmates！

629
00:39:05,457 --> 00:39:06,769
给他们武器！
Give it to 'em！

630
00:39:06,944 --> 00:39:08,059
起来！船是我们的！
Wake up！It's ours！

631
00:39:08,061 --> 00:39:09,174
快一点！
Come on！

632
00:39:09,313 --> 00:39:10,974
起来！让开！
Get up！Off your backside！

633
00:39:12,516 --> 00:39:13,699
你们起来！
Get off your fannies！

634
00:39:13,701 --> 00:39:14,882
给他们武器！
Take it to them，lads！

635
00:39:15,019 --> 00:39:16,850
快帮忙！战斗！
Help me！Fight！

636
00:39:30,401 --> 00:39:31,800
