Jack. 

637
00:39:33,437 --> 00:39:35,752
如果这是梦
If this is a dream，

638
00:39:35,754 --> 00:39:38,067
你可以留着剑和靴子
you can keep the sword and boots on. 

639
00:39:40,211 --> 00:39:41,474
如果不是...
If it's not...

640
00:39:41,476 --> 00:39:42,736
这当然是梦
It's a dream. 

641
00:39:48,352 --> 00:39:49,410
不，才怪！
No，it's not！

642
