...stay out of it. 

647
00:40:25,356 --> 00:40:26,653
碍事

648
00:40:48,145 --> 00:40:49,544
可恶！
Wretch！

649
00:41:19,176 --> 00:41:21,167
是当伙伴还是当敌人！
You're either with us or against us！

650
00:41:21,312 --> 00:41:22,479
我不支持你们
I am not with you，

651
00:41:22,481 --> 00:41:23,645
也不反对你们！
neither am I against you！

652
00:41:23,647 --> 00:41:25,012
他到底要怎么样？
Can he do that？

653
00:41:25,149 --> 00:41:28,175
他本来就没有什么自己的立场
He's religious. I believe it's required. 

654
00:41:33,491 --> 00:41:35,150
奋战到底吧
Fight to the bitter end，

655
00:41:35,152 --> 00:41:36,824
你们这群傻蛋！
you cack-handed deck apes！

656
00:41:48,639 --> 00:41:49,839
抓住他
Take him，men. 

657
00:41:49,841 --> 00:41:51,039
把他绑牢了！
Tie him down tight！

658
00:42:05,789 --> 00:42:07,518
船是我们的了！
The ship is ours！

659
00:42:36,353 --> 00:42:38,583
各位
Gentlemen. 

660
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:49,522
我被搞糊涂了
I be placed in a bewilderment. 

661
00:42:49,633 --> 00:42:51,965
我正在
There I were，

662
00:42:51,966 --> 00:42:54,297
休息着
resting，

663
