Now，we know the answer to that，do we not？

677
00:43:35,879 --> 00:43:39,440
你们这是自寻死路！
Mutineers hang！

678
00:44:29,266 --> 00:44:30,995
船长，我要报告有人叛变
Captain，I wish to report a mutiny. 

679
00:44:31,903 --> 00:44:34,289
我能扳着指头数出来，一个个报给你听
I can name fingers and point names. 

680
00:44:34,271 --> 00:44:35,738
用不着，斯派罗先生
No need，Mr.Sparrow. 

681
00:44:35,873 --> 00:44:37,489
他们是喽啰
They are sheep. 

682
00:44:37,491 --> 00:44:39,104
你，才是主脑
You，their shepherd. 

683
00:44:44,014 --> 00:44:45,362
我有提过
Have I mentioned，sir，

684
00:44:45,364 --> 00:44:46,710
你女儿有多美吗？
what a lovely daughter you have？

685
00:44:47,351 --> 00:44:49,785
那她就是你死前最后的美景了
A fitting last sight for a doomed soul. 

686
00:44:49,953 --> 00:44:51,153
别忘了，父亲
Remember，Father. 

687
00:44:51,155 --> 00:44:52,353
