They do not forget. 

692
00:45:00,497 --> 00:45:02,863
你的船员视你如恶棍
Your crew sees you for the miscreant you are. 

693
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,332
是个懦夫，不管你杀多少人
A coward，no matter how many you slay. 

694
00:45:05,436 --> 00:45:07,870
我又被搞糊涂了
Twice in one day，I find myself in a bewilderment. 

695
00:45:08,005 --> 00:45:10,132
你没有被搞糊涂，你是害怕
You are not bewildered，you are afraid. 

696
00:45:10,841 --> 00:45:11,990
你不敢走向正义
You dare not walk the path of righteousness，

697
00:45:11,991 --> 00:45:13,139
走向光明之路
the way of the light. 

698
00:45:13,310 --> 00:45:17,679
不对，我没那么复杂
No，sir. The truth is it be much simpler than all that.

699
00:45:17,681 --> 00:45:19,378
我是个坏人
I am a bad man. 

700
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:20,582
那，也是
That，too. 

701
00:45:20,718 --> 00:45:22,709
我也许也得杀了你，牧师
I might have to kill you too，catechist. 

702
00:45:22,853 --> 00:45:23,900
不行！
No！

703
00:45:23,902 --> 00:45:25,447
就像她拉丁妈妈
All Latin blood like her mother. 

704
00:45:25,589 --> 00:45:27,682
父亲，求求你
Father，I beg you. 

705
00:45:27,791 --> 00:45:29,046
我又来了
There I be again，

706
00:45:29,047 --> 00:45:31,557
老忘记传教士为什么在这里
forgetting why the missionary is here. 

707
00:45:31,695 --> 00:45:36,098
是我女儿想救赎我仅存的灵魂
My daughter fears for my soul，or what's left of it. 

708
00:45:37,101 --> 00:45:40,764
你真的想救赎我吗，我的孩子？
You truly wish to save me，my child？

709
00:45:40,904 --> 00:45:42,838
每个灵魂都会被救赎
Every soul can be saved. 

710
00:45:43,907 --> 00:45:45,772
真的吗，年轻的牧师？
Be that true，young cleric？

711
00:45:45,909 --> 00:45:46,909
是的
Yes. 

712
00:45:46,911 --> 00:45:49,606
我看虽然救赎你是有一点风险
Though you I sees a bit of a long shot. 

713
00:45:50,614 --> 00:45:52,594
我仍然为这地狱船上
Still，I pray for every unfortunate 

714
00:45:52,595 --> 00:45:54,573
每个不幸的灵魂祈祷
soulon this hell-bound vessel. 

715
00:45:57,121 --> 00:45:59,783
你用你的信仰解除了我的武装
You disarm me with your faith. 

716
00:46:01,158 --> 00:46:02,625
现在是八点！
Eight bells！

717
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:05,752
是哪个不幸的灵魂守了望台？
Which of you unfortunate soulsstood watch？

718
00:46:05,896 --> 00:46:08,376
是我，是我在守望
I did. I stood watch. 

719
00:46:08,378 --> 00:46:10,856
炮手
Gunner. 

720
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:17,639
是你？
You？

721
00:46:18,308 --> 00:46:19,935
是
Aye. 

722
00:46:20,477 --> 00:46:22,274
好吧
Aye. 

723
00:46:22,412 --> 00:46:24,403
厨子
The cook. 

724
00:46:24,515 --> 00:46:27,416
太好了，降下长艇！
Perfect. Lower the longboat！

725
00:46:32,656 --> 00:46:34,647
掉头！
Bring her about！

726
00:46:46,203 --> 00:46:47,716
你为什么要这样做？
Why do you do this？

727
00:46:47,718 --> 00:46:49,229
叛变，我们的法律是清楚的
Mutiny. Our laws be clear. 

728
00:46:49,406 --> 00:46:51,670
我们的法律允许船长法外施恩
Our laws allow the Captain to show leniency. 

729
00:46:51,809 --> 00:46:54,437
我给过他机会决定他的命运
I have given this mana chance to determine his fate，

730
00:46:54,545 --> 00:46:56,240
不是每个人都有的
a gift not afforded to all. 

731
00:47:05,355 --> 00:47:06,822
喔，现在你
Oh，you now. 

732
00:47:08,125 --> 00:47:10,859
有机会来显现你的祈祷的价值了
Chance to show the worth of your prayers. 

733
00:47:10,861 --> 00:47:14,922
祈祷他脱离…邪恶？
Pray he be delivered from... evil？

734
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:24,605
瞄准目标！
Course made！

735
00:47:24,775 --> 00:47:26,606
住手，给他机会，也给你自己...
Stop. Give that man a chance. Give yourself a...

736
00:47:52,336 --> 00:47:55,070
知道我在什么时候最接近造物主？
You know when I feel closest to our Maker？

737
00:47:55,072 --> 00:47:57,070
在我看到苦难，痛苦和悲伤的时候
When I see suffering，pain and anguish. 

738
00:47:57,074 --> 00:47:59,599
这时祂才会显现真正的意图
That's when the true design of this world is revealed. 

739
00:47:59,743 --> 00:48:03,440
我看到是祂在苦难和悲剧发生时
And I see it revealed when in times of hardship and tragedy，

740
00:48:03,580 --> 00:48:05,878
才对需要的人施予仁慈和怜悯
kindness and compassion are shown to those in need. 

741
00:48:06,016 --> 00:48:08,416
也许你该祈祷他不受伤害，是吧？
Perhaps you should pray for him to be unharmed，yes？

742
00:48:08,552 --> 00:48:09,650
他还有机会...
Please，there's still hope...

743
00:48:09,652 --> 00:48:10,747
再开炮！
Again！

744
00:48:23,500 --> 00:48:26,060
其实我对不老泉毫无兴趣
I actually have no interest in the Fountain whatsoever，

745
00:48:26,203 --> 00:48:28,068
如果你心意已定
so，if your heart is set，

746
00:48:28,205 --> 00:48:30,400
