you may drop me off anywhere you like. 

747
00:48:30,540 --> 00:48:32,303
舵手，可以了
That'll be all，Quartermaster. 

748
00:48:35,312 --> 00:48:37,058
你说的话像雾一样
Your words surround you like fog 

749
00:48:37,059 --> 00:48:38,804
让我看不透
and make you hard to see. 

750
00:48:38,949 --> 00:48:42,783
你呢，强大的黑胡子？
And what of you，the mighty Blackbeard？

751
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:44,302
听说你被砍头
Beheaded they say. 

752
00:48:44,304 --> 00:48:47,574
但你的身体还绕着你的船游三圈
Still，your body swam three times around your ship， 

753
00:48:47,576 --> 00:48:49,292
然后爬上船去
then climbed back onboard. 

754
00:48:49,426 --> 00:48:50,723
而现在你好好的
And here you are，

755
00:48:50,724 --> 00:48:52,020
