running scared. 

756
00:48:52,663 --> 00:48:54,381
怕得要命
Scared. 

757
00:48:54,383 --> 00:48:56,099
要找不老泉
To the Fountain. 

758
00:48:56,233 --> 00:48:59,259
舵手有预知能力
The Quartermaster sees things before they happen. 

759
00:48:59,403 --> 00:49:01,560
他预知我的死亡
He has foreseen my death，

760
00:49:01,562 --> 00:49:03,897
所以命运开口了
and so the fates have spoken. 

761
00:49:04,007 --> 00:49:06,373
我的命运已经决定
The threads of destiny woven. 

762
00:49:06,543 --> 00:49:09,478
你太高估命运的力量了
You have a ridiculously high regard for fate，mate. 

763
00:49:09,613 --> 00:49:10,427
那你呢？
And you？

764
00:49:10,429 --> 00:49:11,240
我？
Me？

765
00:49:11,348 --> 00:49:13,498
预知命运我是怀疑的...
I'm skeptical of predicting any future... 

766
00:49:13,500 --> 00:49:15,648
包括我自己
which includes me. 

767
00:49:15,786 --> 00:49:18,687
反抗命运是件傻事
It'd be foolish to battle fate，

768
00:49:18,689 --> 00:49:21,588
但我想冒这个险
but I'd be tempted to cheat it. 

769
00:49:21,692 --> 00:49:23,143
我会找到不老泉
I will reach the Fountain. 

770
00:49:23,145 --> 00:49:24,593
你会带我去
You will lead me. 

771
00:49:27,030 --> 00:49:29,027
那把刀和你搞的
That knife will serve you no better than  

772
00:49:29,028 --> 00:49:31,023
叛变一样没用
the mutiny you devised. 

773
00:49:31,168 --> 00:49:32,965
叛变很有用
Mutiny served me well. 

774
00:49:33,103 --> 00:49:35,037
不是让我见到你了
It gained me an audience with you. 

775
00:49:37,040 --> 00:49:38,268
是啊
Aye. 

776
00:49:39,676 --> 00:49:41,473
我要警告你
To warn you. 

777
00:49:42,446 --> 00:49:44,004
注意你的大副
Regarding your first mate，

778
00:49:44,147 --> 00:49:47,048
