Sir，the woman is consummate in the art of deception. 

783
00:50:04,201 --> 00:50:05,661
我很清楚
I know. 

784
00:50:05,663 --> 00:50:07,162
是我不小心
As I mostly unwittingly 

785
00:50:07,163 --> 00:50:08,661
让她走上这条路
set her on her wicked path. 

786
00:50:08,805 --> 00:50:11,320
虽然我不能说
