the one true good thing I have done in this life，

790
00:50:21,218 --> 00:50:22,549
而你却自称你教坏了她？
and you claim to be the one who corrupted her？

791
00:50:24,021 --> 00:50:28,048
她是纯粹的邪恶化身
Sir，what she is pure evil. 

792
00:50:28,191 --> 00:50:30,591
比野兽更令人害怕
More to be feared than a wild beast. 

793
00:50:30,727 --> 00:50:34,561
又饿又有尖牙的野兽
Hungry wild beast with gnashing teeth. 

794
00:50:34,698 --> 00:50:36,723
报复的，来自地狱的饥饿野兽...
Vengeful，hungry from hell beast...

795
00:50:36,867 --> 00:50:37,948
父亲？
Father？

796
00:50:37,950 --> 00:50:39,028
但是很可爱！
Sweetness！

797
00:50:40,971 --> 00:50:42,529
不必伤害他的，父亲
No need to hurt him，Father. 

798
00:50:42,672 --> 00:50:45,903
他会帮助我们，对吧，杰克？
He will help us. Won't you，Jack？

799
00:50:46,043 --> 00:50:47,909
瞧？到现在
You see？Even now，

800
00:50:47,911 --> 00:50:49,774
她还是关心你的安危
she attends to your welfare，

801
00:50:49,913 --> 00:50:53,474
虽然你一再说她是骗子
giving lie to the claims you make of her. 

802
00:51:01,058 --> 00:51:05,552
你会带我们到不老泉，对吧？
You will lead us to the Fountain. Yes？

803
00:51:06,363 --> 00:51:08,058
换另一个方式说吧
Put another way. 

804
00:51:08,865 --> 00:51:12,266
要是我来不及赶到不老泉...
If I do not make it to the Fountain in time...

805
00:51:13,904 --> 00:51:16,896
...你也去不了
...neither will you. 

806
00:51:19,042 --> 00:51:21,107
我马上仔细看
I'll have a wee look-see at those 

807
00:51:21,108 --> 00:51:23,172
这些航海图，好吧？
charts straight away then，shall I？

808
00:51:26,917 --> 00:51:28,179
长官
Sir. 

809
00:51:31,054 --> 00:51:32,237
什么事？
Aye？

810
00:51:32,239 --> 00:51:33,420
船长，长官
Captain，sir，

811
00:51:33,557 --> 00:51:35,957
长官，我在船员中听到
I am unhappy to report rumors，sir，

812
00:51:36,093 --> 00:51:39,000
关于目的地不好的谣言
among the crew，as to our destination. 

813
00:51:39,463 --> 00:51:41,454
闭上你的嘴给我离开
Shut your trap and make way. 

814
00:51:45,469 --> 00:51:47,284
你想抗命
That's the way of it，then. 

815
00:51:47,286 --> 00:51:49,098
无意冒犯，长官
No disrespect，sir. 

816
00:51:49,906 --> 00:51:51,795
他们怕什么？说出来
What do the men fear？Say it. 

817
00:51:51,797 --> 00:51:52,739
说出那个字
Speak the words. 

818
00:51:53,477 --> 00:51:54,808
白帽湾
Whitecap Bay. 

819
00:51:54,945 --> 00:51:58,073
是啊，白帽湾
Aye，Whitecap Bay. 

820
00:51:58,181 --> 00:52:00,229
所有没用的水手
And every worthless seaman fears the name，

821
00:52:00,230 --> 00:52:02,277
都恐惧这名字
and rightly so，

822
00:52:02,419 --> 00:52:04,915
虽然少数人知道原因或胆敢询问
though few know why or dare to ask. 

823
00:52:04,921 --> 00:52:06,548
传说是真的？
Be the stories true？

824
00:52:06,723 --> 00:52:08,620
吉卜斯，说，是什么让你们动摇了
Say what robs you of your staunch heart，Gibbs，

825
00:52:08,658 --> 00:52:11,821
否则永远留在幻想的领域
or forever leave it to the wider fields of fancy. 

826
00:52:14,498 --> 00:52:16,125
人鱼，船长
Mermaids，Captain. 

827
00:52:16,266 --> 00:52:18,029
是啊，人鱼
Aye. Mermaids. 

828
00:52:18,168 --> 00:52:20,319
大海食尸鬼，魔鬼鱼
Sea ghouls，devil fish，

829
00:52:20,321 --> 00:52:22,470
令人恐惧的是超爱吃人肉
dreadful in hunger for flesh of man. 

830
00:52:22,472 --> 00:52:26,033
我们就是要经过人鱼海域
Mermaid waters，that be our path. 

831
00:52:26,176 --> 00:52:27,768
顾好你的灵魂，吉卜斯
Cling to your soul，Gibbs，

832
00:52:27,878 --> 00:52:31,541
听说人鱼会把人吃到...
as mermaids be given to take the rest...

833
00:52:31,681 --> 00:52:33,114
...只剩骨头
...to the bone. 

834
00:52:34,651 --> 00:52:36,233
冷静！冷静，大伙们！
Steady！Steady，men！

835
00:52:36,234 --> 00:52:37,814
鼓起你们的勇气
Find your courage，

836
00:52:37,954 --> 00:52:39,854
不然就准备恐惧吧！
or be ready to purpose your fear！

837
00:52:39,990 --> 00:52:42,390
自求多福吧！
Save yourselves！

838
00:52:44,961 --> 00:52:46,395
有人落水！
Man overboard！

839
00:52:46,397 --> 00:52:47,828
不是！那是弃船者
Nay！A deserter. 

840
00:52:47,964 --> 00:52:48,846
改变航向
Come about. 

841
00:52:48,848 --> 00:52:49,727
不
Nay！

842
00:52:51,001 --> 00:52:52,335
各位
Gentlemen，

843
00:52:52,337 --> 00:52:54,154
我不会要求你们
I shall not ask any more of  

844
00:52:54,156 --> 00:52:55,971
做办不到的事
any man than what that man can deliver，

845
00:52:55,973 --> 00:52:59,465
但我想问：我们是不是英国的臣民？
but I do ask this：Are we not king's men？

846
00:52:59,576 --> 00:53:01,043
是
Aye. 

847
00:53:01,178 --> 00:53:02,560
那我们是不是国王的好臣民？
On the king's mission？

848
00:53:02,562 --> 00:53:03,942
是
Aye. 

849
00:53:04,114 --> 00:53:06,230
当西班牙佬从旁经过时
I did not note any fear in the eyes 

850
00:53:06,232 --> 00:53:08,346
我在西班牙佬眼中看不到恐惧
of the Spanish as they passed us by. 

851
00:53:08,485 --> 00:53:09,950
你们敢不敢去白帽湾？
Are we not king's men？

852
00:53:09,952 --> 00:53:11,215
敢！
Aye！

853
00:53:11,354 --> 00:53:14,289
现在给我滚回自己的岗位干活！
Aye！Hands all off，and bear away！

854
00:53:14,457 --> 00:53:17,392
直直航向白帽湾！
Stave on ahead to Whitecap Bay！

855
00:53:19,029 --> 00:53:21,395
航向，白帽湾！
Bear on，Whitecap Bay！

856
00:53:35,378 --> 00:53:36,868
来嘛
Come. 

857
00:53:37,013 --> 00:53:38,310
喝点酒？
Little drink？

858
00:53:38,481 --> 00:53:41,712
美酒，音乐，烛光
Wine，music，candlelight. 

859
00:53:41,851 --> 00:53:44,081
这种事我们早就做过，杰克
I think we've traveled down this road before，Jack. 

860
00:53:44,221 --> 00:53:46,052
没错，我们是做过
Yes，we have. 

861
00:53:47,023 --> 00:53:48,422
我记得很清楚
I remember it well. 

862
00:53:50,260 --> 00:53:55,095
缠绕，扭曲和转动，回转，扭动着
Winding，twisting andturning，gyrating，writhing. 

863
00:53:55,232 --> 00:53:57,564
不停地扭动着
Incessant writhing. 

864
00:53:57,701 --> 00:53:59,566
记得圣多明哥吗？
Do you recall Saint Dominique？

865
00:54:01,004 --> 00:54:02,562
拉马提尼克岛
La Martinique. 

866
00:54:02,706 --> 00:54:04,401
在圣多明哥我就想杀你了
I tried to kill you in Saint Dominique. 

867
00:54:04,541 --> 00:54:06,304
无所谓啦
Either or. 

868
00:54:07,110 --> 00:54:09,135
对一位大副几乎没有恰当的
Hardly appropriate for a first mate. 

869
00:54:09,279 --> 00:54:12,737
我是你的第一次吗？我总想知道
Was I the first？I've often wondered. 

870
00:54:12,882 --> 00:54:17,114
当你有欲望时真迷人，杰克
You can be so charming when you want something，Jack. 

871
00:54:17,254 --> 00:54:19,745
窍门是找出你想要什么
The trick is finding out what. 

872
00:54:20,857 --> 00:54:22,950
事实，是什么？
The truth，then，is it？

873
00:54:23,660 --> 00:54:26,151
黑胡子已经达到他的目的
Blackbeard has served his purpose. 

874
00:54:26,296 --> 00:54:28,628
你和我一起去不老泉
You and I can go to the Fountain together，

875
00:54:28,765 --> 00:54:31,825
一起沐浴在不老泉
where we shall bathe one another in equal shares of fame

876
00:54:31,968 --> 00:54:33,993
尽情享受各种欢愉
and other assorted debaucheries. 

877
00:54:34,137 --> 00:54:37,129
而我告诉你不老泉的仪式
And I'll tell youthe ritual of the Fountain. 

878
00:54:37,274 --> 00:54:40,107
对，异教的仪式
Yes. The profane ritual. 

879
00:54:42,812 --> 00:54:45,007
我能信任你吗，杰克？
Can I trust you，Jack？

880
00:54:45,148 --> 00:54:47,367
我需要你站在我这边
I need you on my side. 

881
00:54:47,369 --> 00:54:49,585
最亲爱的安洁莉卡
Oh，my dearest Angelica. 

882
00:54:49,686 --> 00:54:53,144
我们是神偷侠侣
You and I are asthick as thieves，love. 

883
00:54:53,290 --> 00:54:55,520
告诉我那个仪式
Tell me the rules. 

884
00:54:57,661 --> 00:55:01,324
不老泉的泉水
Water from the Fountain of Youth. 

885
00:55:03,166 --> 00:55:06,602
人鱼闪亮的泪水
The shimmering tear of a mermaid. 

886
00:55:06,703 --> 00:55:10,036
庞塞德莱昂的银杯
The silver chalices of Ponce de Leon. 

887
00:55:11,975 --> 00:55:13,704
只要用这些东西...
With these items...

888
00:55:13,843 --> 00:55:14,907
怎样？
Yes？

889
00:55:14,909 --> 00:55:15,970
用这些东西
With these items，

890
00:55:16,112 --> 00:55:19,513
你就能得到另一个人的全部岁月
you may take all the years of life from another，Jack. 

891
00:55:21,785 --> 00:55:23,616
杰克，你知道这意味着什么
You know what that means. 

892
00:55:23,720 --> 00:55:26,655
我们俩不能单独去
We cannot go alone，you and I. 

893
00:55:26,790 --> 00:55:29,054
仪式需要一名牺牲者
The ritual requires a victim. 

894
00:55:30,794 --> 00:55:32,728
这真不幸
That is unfortunate. 

895
00:55:32,730 --> 00:55:34,662
是啊
Yes，it is. 

896
00:55:35,665 --> 00:55:38,532
我对不老泉的欲望都没了
I find my desire for the Fountaing reatly lessened. 

897
00:55:39,936 --> 00:55:42,564
不过船上有你想要的东西
But there is something on board you do want. 

898
00:55:48,345 --> 00:55:49,710
黑胡子来了怎么办？
What about Blackbeard？

899
00:55:49,846 --> 00:55:51,644
他在海图室
He's in the chart room. 

900
00:55:51,646 --> 00:55:53,441
我们要快点
We'll have to be quick. 

901
00:56:02,525 --> 00:56:05,119
他把每艘船当成战利品保存着
He keeps each ship as a prize. 

902
00:56:06,896 --> 00:56:09,126
只要你帮我
You help me，

903
00:56:09,128 --> 00:56:11,356
我保证让你挑你要的船
and I promise you your pick. 

904
00:56:11,501 --> 00:56:14,902
虽然我知道你会挑哪一艘
Though I think I know the one you will choose. 

905
00:56:20,777 --> 00:56:23,268
黑珍珠号在瓶子里？
The Black Pearl in a bottle？

906
00:56:23,413 --> 00:56:25,142
黑珍珠号怎么会在瓶子里？
Why is the Black Pearl in a bottle？

907
00:56:30,920 --> 00:56:33,787
那只猴子缩小了还是那么讨厌
He's even more annoying in miniature. 

908
00:56:33,923 --> 00:56:35,937
我们就这么说定了咯，杰克？
Do we have a deal，Jack？

909
00:56:35,939 --> 00:56:37,950
安洁莉卡，我了解你
Angelica，I know you. 

910
00:56:38,094 --> 00:56:40,961
你不会偷走无辜者的生命
You are not going to steal the life of some innocent man. 

911
00:56:41,531 --> 00:56:43,829
独腿者的怎么样？
What about the one-legged man？

912
00:56:46,069 --> 00:56:47,730
杰克，我需要岁月
I need years，Jack. 

913
00:56:49,539 --> 00:56:51,257
不是为我
Not for me. 

914
00:56:51,259 --> 00:56:52,975
是为了我的父亲
For my father. 

915
00:56:55,578 --> 00:56:57,910
我真的是黑胡子的女儿
I am truly the daughter of Blackbeard. 

916
00:56:58,915 --> 00:57:01,110
你迷失在自己的假话了
You've fallen for your own con，love. 

917
00:57:01,251 --> 00:57:03,515
不是的，他是我的父亲
No，he is my father. 

918
00:57:03,686 --> 00:57:05,381
我对你说的假话不全是假的
The lies I told you were not lies. 

919
00:57:07,157 --> 00:57:10,058
你对我说的假话都是真的？
You lied to me by telling me the truth？

920
00:57:10,160 --> 00:57:11,173
对
Yes. 

921
00:57:11,175 --> 00:57:12,185
这招厉害
That's very good. 

922
00:57:12,362 --> 00:57:13,579
我能用这招吗？
May I use that？

923
00:57:13,581 --> 00:57:14,796
少来，我肯定你会的
I'm sure you will，anyway. 

924
00:57:14,931 --> 00:57:17,297
我当然会罗
Of course I will. 

925
00:57:17,434 --> 00:57:20,130
所以，你不会放弃这个搜寻？
So，will you not give up this quest？

926
00:57:20,737 --> 00:57:22,301
我想要父爱，杰克
I want a father，Jack. 

927
00:57:22,303 --> 00:57:23,865
我不曾有过
I haven't had one. 

928
00:57:25,108 --> 00:57:28,407
安洁莉卡，你的父亲，黑胡子...
Angelica，your father，Blackbeard...

929
00:57:29,946 --> 00:57:31,311
...他很邪恶
...he is evil，

930
00:57:31,448 --> 00:57:33,643
而且有机会他会杀了你
and he will kill you given the chance. 

931
00:57:33,783 --> 00:57:35,330
他是无法被救赎的
He cannot be saved. 

932
00:57:35,332 --> 00:57:39,214
你又凭什么来规定救赎界限？
And who are you to set the limits on redemption？

933
00:57:39,389 --> 00:57:41,839
你偷走了我的青春
You stole years of my life，Jack. 

934
00:57:41,841 --> 00:57:42,688
这是你欠我的
You owe me. 

935
00:57:42,826 --> 00:57:45,886
你这是在自己找死
And you are en route to getting yourself killed，

936
00:57:46,062 --> 00:57:48,360
我不想袖手旁观
and I am not inclined to stand by and watch. 

937
00:57:48,498 --> 00:57:52,229
白帽湾到了！
Whitecap Bay！

938
00:57:57,340 --> 00:57:59,086
全员集合！
All hands on deck！

939
00:57:59,088 --> 00:58:00,832
准备上长艇！
Set to the longboats！

940
00:58:04,814 --> 00:58:05,838
把渔网摆平！
Lay 'em out flat！

941
00:58:06,516 --> 00:58:07,617
不要打结
No tangles. 

942
00:58:07,619 --> 00:58:11,317
弄漂亮点迎接我们美丽的娇客
Make 'em look pretty for our dainty guests. 

943
00:58:11,454 --> 00:58:13,354
我们需要灯光
We're gonna need light. 

944
00:58:13,356 --> 00:58:15,254
很强的灯光
A lot of light. 

945
00:58:17,026 --> 00:58:18,050
跟我来！
Come！

946
00:58:39,849 --> 00:58:42,460
闻到了吗？鲸鱼油，
Smell that？Whale oil. 

947
00:58:42,462 --> 00:58:45,082
燃烧的火光像是上帝的奇蹟
Stuff burns like a miracle from God. 

948
00:58:45,221 --> 00:58:47,087
你能点燃灯塔吗？
Can you make it work？

949
00:58:47,089 --> 00:58:48,952
英国佬制造的
Made by the English. 

950
00:58:49,125 --> 00:58:50,217
我们就不要期望太大了
Let's not get our hopes up. 

951
00:59:01,237 --> 00:59:03,337
月亮新的周期
The old moon in the arms of the new one. 

952
00:59:03,339 --> 00:59:05,473
夏季第一次开始时
First of the summer. 

953
00:59:05,475 --> 00:59:08,706
最适合搜集人鱼的泪水
Perfect for hunting a mermaid's tear. 

954
00:59:20,957 --> 00:59:22,925
我们完蛋了
We're doomed. 

955
00:59:22,927 --> 00:59:24,893
她们会被人工灯光吸引
They be drawn to man-made light. 

956
00:59:25,028 --> 00:59:26,376
鲨鱼？
Sharks？

957
00:59:26,378 --> 00:59:27,724
比鲨鱼更可怕，小子
Worse than sharks，boy. 

958
00:59:27,864 --> 00:59:30,389
一小时后人鱼就会来袭
There'll be mermaids upon us within the hour，

959
00:59:30,533 --> 00:59:32,262
你们记住我的话
you mark my words. 

960
00:59:32,264 --> 00:59:33,991
我们就是诱饵
And we're the bait. 

961
00:59:38,641 --> 00:59:40,473
我听说从人鱼那得到亲吻
I heard it said a kiss from a mermaid 

962
00:59:40,474 --> 00:59:42,304
就可以保证水手不会淹死
protects a sailor from drowning. 

963
00:59:42,445 --> 00:59:44,379
别傻了！
Don't be a fool！

964
00:59:44,381 --> 00:59:46,313
孩子，人鱼都是女的
Mermaids are all female，son，

965
00:59:46,449 --> 00:59:49,247
而且个个美如天仙
and lovely as a dream of heaven. 

966
00:59:49,385 --> 00:59:53,651
到了搅拌奶油的时间
But when it comes time to churn butter，so to speak，

967
00:59:53,790 --> 00:59:55,781
她们就从长艇
they snatch a sailor out of a boat

968
00:59:55,925 --> 00:59:58,951
或甲板上抓走一个水手
or off the deck of a ship，have their way，

969
00:59:59,095 --> 01:00:01,564
然后这些水手被拉到海底
and then the sailors are pulled to bottom 

970
01:00:01,565 --> 01:00:04,032
被淹死然后被吃掉
and drowned and eaten. 

971
01:00:04,467 --> 01:00:07,925
要不然，有时，是另一种结局
Or，sometimes，the other way around. 

972
01:00:09,272 --> 01:00:10,552
唱歌
Sing. 

973
01:00:10,554 --> 01:00:11,832
什么？
What？

974
01:00:13,209 --> 01:00:15,336
她们喜欢听人唱歌
