I don't like toads. 

1379
01:32:48,178 --> 01:32:49,896
你在干嘛？
What are you doing？

1380
01:32:49,898 --> 01:32:51,614
安排脱逃路线啊
Planning an escape route. 

1381
01:32:51,749 --> 01:32:53,797
你不都是这样做的？
Isn't that how you do it？

1382
01:32:53,799 --> 01:32:55,845
是啊
Yes. 

1383
01:32:55,953 --> 01:32:57,517
但有时候我会...
Or sometimes I just...

1384
01:32:57,518 --> 01:32:59,081
