I had no part in this. 

1401
01:35:27,705 --> 01:35:29,138
放了她，你不需要她了
Let her go. You don't need her now. 

1402
01:35:29,306 --> 01:35:32,241
放了她？不行
Let her go？No. 

1403
01:35:32,376 --> 01:35:33,872
把她绑紧
Secure her bonds. 

1404
01:35:33,874 --> 01:35:35,368
让她自生自灭
We leave her with her own. 

1405
01:35:44,922 --> 01:35:46,913
你的逃跑路线呢？
How's that escape route working？

1406
01:35:47,057 --> 01:35:50,026
现在只能靠你随机应变啦
Here's your chance to improvise. 

1407
01:35:50,127 --> 01:35:51,458
我也想呀
I'm attempting it. 

1408
01:35:51,595 --> 01:35:54,428
只要弄松一只手就行
I might be able to get a hand loose. 

1409
01:35:54,565 --> 01:35:56,829
喔，你藏了刀子，太好了
Oh，you got a knife. That's very good. 

1410
01:35:57,935 --> 01:35:59,459
比那更好
Better. 

1411
01:36:04,908 --> 01:36:06,170
我也要一支
I want one of those. 

1412
01:36:10,881 --> 01:36:12,997
敬复仇
Here's to revenge. 

1413
01:36:12,998 --> 01:36:15,113
甜蜜的复仇
Sweet and clear. 

1414
01:36:15,252 --> 01:36:17,482
什么复仇？
Revenge？

1415
01:36:17,484 --> 01:36:19,712
老巴，行了，别装了
Come，come，Hector. 

1416
01:36:19,823 --> 01:36:21,256
如果你想要圣盃
If you wanted the chalices，

1417
01:36:21,391 --> 01:36:24,087
