Cheap theatrical facade. 

1421
01:36:35,305 --> 01:36:36,739
我才不信
I'm not buying it. 

1422
01:36:36,741 --> 01:36:38,172
那天晚上你又不在场
You weren't there that night. 

1423
01:36:38,308 --> 01:36:40,225
失去黑珍珠号的那晚
When the Pearl was lost？

1424
01:36:40,227 --> 01:36:42,142
