And wrapping around me leg. 

1436
01:37:20,751 --> 01:37:23,151
但我双手是自由的而且手里还握着剑
But me arms were free and me sword was to hand. 

1437
01:37:23,287 --> 01:37:26,814
我的船由我主宰，不是黑胡子
I am the master of me ship，not Blackbeard. 

1438
01:37:26,957 --> 01:37:30,449
我的生命由我主宰，不是黑胡子
I am the master of my fate，not Blackbeard. 

1439
01:37:31,461 --> 01:37:33,827
所以我做了我该做的事
So I did what needed done. 

1440
01:37:40,671 --> 01:37:42,605
我活下来了
I survived. 

1441
01:37:44,174 --> 01:37:48,372
