for a chance at Blackbeard. 

1446
01:38:00,057 --> 01:38:01,542
不是右手？
Not your right？

1447
01:38:01,544 --> 01:38:03,026
我需要好用的右手
I need me good arm

1448
01:38:03,160 --> 01:38:07,824
把毒剑刺进他的心脏
to drive my poisoned blade through his heart. 

1449
01:38:08,799 --> 01:38:11,233
老兄，你会有机会的
I'll see you get the chance，mate. 

1450
01:39:29,980 --> 01:39:31,311
俘虏逃走了
The prisoner's escaping. 

1451
01:39:38,588 --> 01:39:41,284
他逃走了！散开！找到他！
He's escaping！Fan out！Find him！

1452
01:39:41,425 --> 01:39:42,517
走！快走！
Go！Go！

1453
01:39:44,594 --> 01:39:47,461
别开枪！我要抓活的！
Hold your fire！I want him alive！

1454
01:39:55,672 --> 01:39:57,640
我觉得那就是信号了
I figured that was the signal. 

1455
01:40:40,717 --> 01:40:42,463
快走！准备出发！
Go！Prepare to move out！

1456
01:40:42,465 --> 01:40:44,209
敌人很快就会找到我们
The enemy is soon upon us. 

1457
01:40:45,956 --> 01:40:47,424
杰克，抱歉没拿到圣盃
I'm sorry about the chalices，Jack，

1458
01:40:47,425 --> 01:40:48,891
但我在赶时间
but I've an appointment to keep. 

1459
01:40:49,026 --> 01:40:50,522
我不会回去拿的
I'll not be going back. 

1460
01:40:50,524 --> 01:40:52,018
没必要
No need. 

1461
01:40:52,162 --> 01:40:53,675
要不要来一杯？
Shall we have a drink？

1462
01:40:53,677 --> 01:40:55,188
我们去不老泉喝
We'll drink at the Fountain. 

1463
01:41:13,550 --> 01:41:15,331
为什么每次见面
How is it we can never meet without  

1464
01:41:15,332 --> 01:41:17,111
你都拿着东西指着我？
you pointing something at me？

1465
01:41:18,321 --> 01:41:20,221
斯派罗，你把圣盃带来了？
You brought the chalices，Sparrow？

1466
01:41:20,357 --> 01:41:22,951
是的，喂！
Aye. Oi！

1467
01:41:26,430 --> 01:41:27,994
你还带了个朋友
I see you brought a friend. 

1468
01:41:27,996 --> 01:41:29,558
是的
I did. 

1469
01:41:29,699 --> 01:41:32,930
独腿者，在附近？
And the one-legged man，he is near. Aye？

1470
01:41:33,070 --> 01:41:34,469
是的
Aye. 

1471
01:41:35,272 --> 01:41:36,296
好了...
Now...

1472
01:41:36,440 --> 01:41:37,857
在我把它们拿给你之前
Before I go just handing them over，

1473
