不，那是第二个
No，no，that's secondly. 

1478
01:41:44,114 --> 01:41:46,378
第一个，你发誓
Firstly，upon your word，

1479
01:41:46,483 --> 01:41:48,474
不伤害安洁莉卡
you will bring no harm to Angelica. 

1480
01:41:48,618 --> 01:41:50,984
斯派罗，我不会向你这种人发誓
I'll make no vows to the likes of you，Sparrow. 

1481
01:41:51,121 --> 01:41:53,589
不过答应你不伤害她
But it costs me nothing to admit

1482
01:41:53,723 --> 01:41:56,590
对我没有损失
that she was never in harm's way. 

1483
01:41:57,227 --> 01:41:59,422
