你不知道地点
you don't know where you're going. 

1522
01:45:15,425 --> 01:45:18,258
俗话说，重要的是旅程不是结果
It is not the destination so much as the journey，they say. 

1523
01:45:19,462 --> 01:45:20,929
圣盃，拜托
Chalices，if you please. 

1524
01:45:32,942 --> 01:45:34,466
